  "texts": [
    "To assess whether participants could correctly identify the source (human vs. computer) of the passages, the second part of the survey asked: \"Which response was generated by a computer?\"",
    "(Response A or B).",
    "We also assessed their confidence in that choice on a 5-point Likert-type scale from \"not at all confident\" (1) to \"extremely confident\" (5).",
    "We also included a structured question to probe participants' beliefs about how they could distinguish between the human and computer passages.",
    "It stated: \"If you noticed differences between the human and computer responses, in which ways did they seem to differ?"
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}